snippet.title: Mix and Game Jam 2019 - World Minigolf
snippet.description:
Our submission for the 2019 Mix and Game Jam! 
Theme: Dimension Change

World Minigolf takes traditional mini golf and warps it around a sphere!

Credits: 
Programming, Shaders: Dexter André Osiander
3D: Bjørnar Børsheim
Textures / UI: Ingvild Grotløkken
Audio: Niklas Gløsen
